00:17:23,392 --> 00:17:23,472
And

302
00:17:24,918 --> 00:17:27,824
That with thinking, with the qualia of thinking,

303
00:17:27,924 --> 00:17:30,330
actually kind of resembles, for most of us anyway,

304
00:17:30,610 --> 00:17:32,655
the qualia of voice, right?

305
00:17:32,675 --> 00:17:33,857
It feels like a voice in our head,

306
00:17:33,877 --> 00:17:35,080
which is kind of interesting.

307
00:17:36,132 --> 00:17:40,796
So what makes the meditation trance different is not only that it's occurring on this deeper

308
00:17:40,816 --> 00:17:45,980
layer of our experience, but from this deeper layer of experience, where the trance is embedded,

309
00:17:46,521 --> 00:17:51,545
that trance in turn affects the narrative mind by helping us become aware of it.

310
00:17:52,245 --> 00:17:56,328
And once we become aware of fluctuations in the narrative mind, the trance in our lower

