00:21:04,603 --> 00:21:08,805
A great example of this is if a player's existing habit

372
00:21:08,825 --> 00:21:10,926
of trying to control the world might interfere

373
00:21:11,286 --> 00:21:12,807
with a trance you're trying to give them

