00:22:33,609 --> 00:22:37,551
and maybe all video games provide a structure for the player to project

405
00:22:37,631 --> 00:22:38,811
their sense of self into.

406
00:22:39,172 --> 00:22:39,932
My avatar,

407
00:22:41,333 --> 00:22:41,373
uh...

