00:23:31,059 --> 00:23:34,579
and you intuitively know it fits on your hand and you might try it on,

421
00:23:35,039 --> 00:23:37,740
if you see something that looks like a ham,

422
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:39,360
you're less likely to try it on your hand.

423
00:23:40,181 --> 00:23:43,681
But we can design gloves that fit your hand really neatly, like Mario does,

424
00:23:44,541 --> 00:23:47,802
or we can design gloves that fit your hand in kind of an awkward way

425
00:23:47,822 --> 00:23:50,723
and make you practice a slightly altered way of being.

426
00:23:51,858 --> 00:23:53,299
And you could do that without going all the way

427
00:23:53,339 --> 00:23:55,340
into the sort of techno-dellic craziness I'm about to describe.

